STRUCTURE: tarotAI Python Package
=================================

This file describes the folder structure of the `tarotAI` project.

------------------------------------------------------------

Root Directory
--------------

Contains the project metadata, packaging configuration, and documentation.

Files:
- .gitignore          → Git exclusions
- LICENSE             → Project license
- MANIFEST.in         → Specifies data files to include in the package
- pyproject.toml      → Modern build configuration for pip
- setup.py            → Legacy setuptools configuration
- README.md           → Project description
- ROADMAP.md          → Future plans and features
- STRUCTURE           → This file (explaining project structure)
- config/             → External runtime settings (not part of the package)
    ├── .env
    └── settings.toml

------------------------------------------------------------

tarotai/ (Main Python Package)
------------------------------

This is the actual pip-installable package. Contains all application logic, configs, and data.

Subfolders and files:

- tarotai/
    ├── __pycache__/           → Python bytecode (ignored)
    │
    ├── config/                → Package-level configuration handling
    │   ├── __init__.py
    │   ├── loader.py          → Loads and parses settings
    │   └── settings.toml      → Default package configuration
    │
    ├── core/                  → Core logic and domain models
    │   ├── __init__.py
    │   ├── classCard.py       → Card class and behavior
    │   ├── classSpread.py     → Spread class and logic
    │   ├── interpreter.py     → Logic to interpret a spread of cards
    │   └── tarotAI_functions.py → Additional helper functions
    │
    └── data/                  → Static JSON data bundled with the package
        ├── __init__.py
        ├── cards.json         → Card definitions and meanings
        └── spreads.json       → Spread layouts and descriptions

------------------------------------------------------------

tests/ (Unit Tests)
-------------------

Contains test scripts to validate core functionality.

Directory:
- tests/
    └── test_*.py              → Your test files go here (e.g., test_card.py)

------------------------------------------------------------

Notes
-----

- `cards.json` and `spreads.json` are included in the final package using `MANIFEST.in`.
- The `config/` folder outside `tarotai/` is for external runtime use (.env, etc).
- Python modules follow `snake_case` naming.
- The project supports both editable (`pip install -e .`) and built installations.

------------------------------------------------------------

End of STRUCTURE
